WEBVTT

1
01:08:31.930 --> 01:08:35.550 
毫无理由相信这些具有敌意嘛
There's no reason to believe their intentions are hostile.

2
01:08:35.930 --> 01:08:39.420 
为什么总迂腐地认为外星人是坏蛋呢？
Why is it the egghead position that aliens are always benign?

3
01:08:40.330 --> 01:08:41.890 
我们对他们不构成威胁
We pose no threat to them.

4
01:08:42.100 --> 01:08:44.660 
好比我们兴师动众去东非
It'd be like us going out of our way

5
01:08:44.940 --> 01:08:46.630 
消灭蚂蚁山上的微生物
to destroy microbes on an anthill.

6
01:08:46.840 --> 01:08:48.300 
有趣的类比
Interesting analogy.

7
01:08:48.910 --> 01:08:52.840 
而我们果真消灭蚂蚁山上的几个微生物  你会觉得内疚吗？
How guilty would we feel if we destroyed a few microbes on an anthill?

8
01:08:53.080 --> 01:08:54.200 
我希望你是正确的
I hope you're right.

9
01:08:54.550 --> 01:08:55.570 
真的
I really do.

10
01:08:55.780 --> 01:08:59.240 
但是  我有责任消除美国人民的任何威胁
But my job is to protect American lives from any threat

11
01:08:59.450 --> 01:09:01.580 
因此我必定要做最坏的打算
so I am obligated to assume the worst.

12
01:09:01.820 --> 01:09:03.810 
是的  我不能不同意
Yes, and I am forced to agree with you.

